rComments: Prof. Triverio is a wonderful professor. It is evident that he cares about his students' education, especially when you approach him after a lecture to ask questions. His writing is very neat, as are the rest of his lectures. Overall, he is calm and professional.
Great lectures, write down everything he writes on the board and study off them. A+
Real great guy. Made me like circuits in general more. Always did a bunch of example problems.
Had him for ECE259 a few years back. Real nice guy, lectures are very clear.
